      <dc:title>Typewritten letter from Lamberg to Julius Zappert (Verein zur Speisung), dated June
        30, 1924</dc:title>

      <dcterms:created>1924-06-30T12:00:00Z</dcterms:created>
      <dcterms:dateSubmitted>2016-10-21</dcterms:dateSubmitted>
      <dc:description>The letter quotes that of the Akademie für Musik to the Verein zur Speisung,
        and requests transfer of sum of money tothe Akademie.</dc:description>
      <dc:subject>Schreiben; letter; Zuschrift; letter; testamentarisch; testimentary; Verfügung;
        decree; Betrag; sum; Stiftung; endowment; Zinsenerträgnisse; income from interest;
        Kompositionsschüler; composition pupil; Ableben; death; Entscheidung; adjudication;
        Stipendien; stipends; Verleihung; award; Ternavorschläge; slate of candidates; Berufung;
        reference</dc:subject>




      <marcrel:correspondent key="entity-000502">Ernst Lamberg</marcrel:correspondent>
